      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "REAL BONNIE (4) is a progressive type who recorded her 4th career win last time out (29.57) at this track. Strike rate this course and distance strong having won three of five tries. Ran the fastest time on the program in her latest win. Well placed and can measure up. IRINKA LINDSAY (2) was safely held last time out, finishing seventh at this track over 515m behind Weffalee Lee Lee (30.52) in a Grade 4/5. Leading chance. DAISY'S CHARM (8) has mixed form recently, finishing seventh (30.39) in a Grade 5 at this track latest but did run well two back when in the frame. Safe beginner but wide box to overcome and will need some luck. Can feature with the right run. SUNSHINE RHONDA (1) is worth another chance despite missing the top-three here most recently.",
